&gt; &gt; is a coming together of all entities interested in mankind.
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt; &quot;The interests are various.
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt;
&gt; &gt; &quot;We, The Seven of the Rainbow
